The paper deals with communication systems and their optimization, which falls under the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) categories. The use of deep neural networks (DNNs) in the proposed algorithm suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also addresses the issue of resource allocation, which is a key concern in control systems (cs.SY).
